<p>We also had some monitors which used to do a fair bit of shooting one of them was armed with a 14 inch gun  she used to make a fair row when she was shooting.<br/>The sunsets at this time of year Dec. were even more beautiful than those of the summer months, they were something lovely, &amp; will never be forgotten by me.<br/>I saw a Frenchman do a daring thing one day he had been flying pretty low over the Turkish positions &amp; they were shooting like mad at him with machine gun, rifle, &amp; anti-aircraft guns but they couldn't hit him, after he had finished his work he mounted up fairly high</p>
